		<td><b>Re: Games that used the window for special effects?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Contra (Operation C in North America) I think is another one that uses the Window layer for a large platform, and possibly other large objects.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


